{"tid":23874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又黎估國家] 美女子遭五人輪姦","createTime":"2016-12-05T08:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T09:37:33.000Z","uid":44562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffed4c9e78c94f67e4d0dee1b45a62d784c7de49","tid":23874,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%8E%E9%81%8A%E8%90%BD%E8%97%A5-%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%81%AD%E4%BA%94%E4%BA%BA%E8%BC%AA%E5%A7%A6-221113571.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25B0%258E%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%2590%25BD%25E8%2597%25A5-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%2581%25AD%25E4%25BA%2594%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E5%25A7%25A6-221113571.html&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ac9cc2a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%8E%E9%81%8A%E8%90%BD%E8%97%A5-%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%81%AD%E4%BA%94%E4%BA%BA%E8%BC%AA%E5%A7%A6-221113571.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】一名美國女子報警稱，今年四月造訪印度首都新德里時，在一家頂級酒店遭人輪姦。<br />\n　　新德里警方上周六接獲女子直接報案後，啟動正式調查。這名女子目前人在美國，最初是透過一個美國非政府組織以電子郵件與印度警方聯繫。印度媒體引述警方消息人士報道，這名女子四月造訪印度，遭人輪暴後提前結束旅程。<br />\n　　女子指控印度導遊給了她一瓶被尖物刺穿的瓶裝水，接着與另外四名她認識的人在酒店房內輪姦她。報道稱：「她說，喝了瓶子里的水後，開始感到暈眩，接着另外四名男子進入她的房間並將門鎖了起來。」警方目前正確認這名女子的時間表並追蹤嫌犯，包括檢視酒店監視器畫面。印度觀光客遭遇性侵事件頻傳，數個西方國家已針對這項風險對遊客發出警告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬼國強暴停不了, 點解仲會有女仔去旅遊 ??"},{"pid":"6902fee100afefada3c0a6d5f751bd29cafe24fe","tid":23874,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:52:22.000Z","msg":"唔好話女<br />\n男人都驚<br />\n幾個gay嘅唔洗迷暈你<br />\n直接的你入草叢老強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fcf596f1ce70b01b976c899e175f1b65d1862d","tid":23874,"uid":35176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:55:47.000Z","msg":"印度真係...我都唔知可以點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a7e027ff1b57173cc707c737379c8edf94c815","tid":23874,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"炸平佢算啦"},{"pid":"b49dbea3c16c12a832b284ffceeabc99883212f8","tid":23874,"uid":41257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:57:54.000Z","msg":"估中<br />\n<br />\n女人真喺唔好去印度"},{"pid":"038b91381e7c6e228e0c1f427903f183d907f6da","tid":23874,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"估中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得印度佬有年比人強姦案唔制止仲要幫手"},{"pid":"a5af1ac66c9ee335f237093bce439351f6501c4f","tid":23874,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc65a912b2979295b5898dd2b99c2bad25d6a5fd","tid":23874,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"垃圾差"},{"pid":"24d9d6064e2a31138c808266dfed904cfcbdb361","tid":23874,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:37:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}